      "comment": "BAREFOOT ZULU (5) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing sixth (30.56) last time in a Special conditions race at The Meadows. Form at the trip sound including seven wins. Form from his last run is proving strong. Can atone. URANA PARALLAX (3) was in the minor money with a useful 34.19, finishing second in a Grade 4/5 at Sandown last start. Harder here but expected to feature again. PAW PHELPS (4) jumped from a middle draw last time and could manage only fourth and beaten 4 lengths (34.96) at The Meadows. Returns to a course where he has performed well. Likely to play a prominent role. BLUER THAN BLUE (1) was well fancied last time on the strength of his recent form but could only manage second (28.57) at Bendigo. Ran one of the fastest times on the program last start despite finishing in the minors. Overdue and expected to feature again.",
